{"tid":398777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉軚) 班農: 習近平是英明的領袖， 特朗普非常尊重習近平","createTime":"2017-09-13T12:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T03:13:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77ed366c8e933f89ec14966b0472371ef81f5e08","tid":398777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.cn.nytimes.com/world/20170913/steve-bannon-trump-hong-kong/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cn.nytimes.com%2Fworld%2F20170913%2Fsteve-bannon-trump-hong-kong%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=K%2BrjvxT0%2FZuN7sZZp0RS3MP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=082ab3ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.cn.nytimes.com/world/20170913/steve-bannon-trump-hong-kong/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n班農訪港不再直言批評中國，改口盛讚習近平<br />\n<br />\n2017年9月13日<br />\n香港&mdash;&mdash;斯蒂芬&middot;K&middot;班農(Stephen K. Bannon)在白宮工作時，曾幫助打造了川普總統把美國經濟問題歸咎於中國的民族主義言論。<br />\n<br />\n如今，在離開政府不到一個月後，曾經擔任川普首席策略師的班農，應一家受中國政府控制的公司之邀來到香港，在這裡，他將中國國家主席習近平稱為一位英明領袖。<br />\n.........<br />\n<br />\n據那兩位參加了這場持續了一個多小時的午餐的投資者說，班農在用餐期間對在場的人說，川普對習近平有著高度尊重，並認為兩位領導人可以找到解決朝鮮危機的辦法。那兩人要求匿名，因為他們沒有獲得公開討論此事的授權。"},{"pid":"c7664527890840aaf10fe4718196e413a7b4153a","tid":398777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cd062c332d851f385a9d8f5667bffc00922d0b","tid":398777,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ade68dad5c56fc0c90acb362abdd391fdb78dbf","tid":398777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中信證券出錢請佢黎，大家知咩事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a84abef9c1b683e6af1c1a3dda9a0239631c40","tid":398777,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:35:07.000